<item>
            <title>[WICKET-6988] String.format used in JS generation leads to errors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6988</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In case system locale is set to Arabic (&lt;tt&gt;ar-EG&lt;/tt&gt; for ex.)&lt;br/&gt;
Numbers are being printed using Arabic symbols, which is wrong in timeouts for ex.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;here is an example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
(function(){Wicket.Timer.set(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;idb3.0&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, function(){Wicket.Ajax.ajax({&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;u&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;./.?4-1.0-main~container-main&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;c&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;idb3&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;dep&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:[function(attrs){&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; Wicket.BrowserInfo.collect()}]});}, &#1637;&#1632;);})()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NOTE &lt;tt&gt;&#1637;&#1632;&lt;/tt&gt; is printed instead of &lt;tt&gt;50&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The cause is &lt;tt&gt;String.format(pattern, args...)&lt;/tt&gt; which will use system default locale&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll try to hunt such issues one-by-one&lt;/p&gt;</description>
